# meetings/

## What goes here
- Scheduled events with a date and participants
- Calls, syncs, reviews, or any time-bound gathering

## What does NOT go here
- Extracted entities from meetings — people go to `people/`, decisions to `decisions/`
- Raw transcript dumps (extract structured signals first)

## Primary Home Test
File here if the event has a specific date and participants.

## Naming Rule
`YYYY-MM-DD-meeting-name.md`. Example: `2026-04-17-investor-sync.md`

## Required Sections
- Executive Summary (purpose, outcome)
- Bias Check
- Participants (linked to people/)
- Key Decisions
- Action Items
- Timeline Evidence
